Products.Name: Helga's Wholemeal Wraps
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Helga's Wholemeal Wraps' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
Helga's Wholemeal Wraps are thin, round and flat. They are 10 inches in diameter, a light brown colour with visible bran flakes, golden brown toast marks and have a wheaty aroma & flavour. They are very soft and pliable texture making it a multipurpose wrap.

Helga’s bakers begin with care by selecting the best quality ingredients, those that bring out the best taste in each other. From mixing, proving, pressing and baking, we allow their true flavours to shine through in our wraps.

WHY NOT TRY?
Use wraps as dippers, chips or crackers. Cut into triangles or squares and spray or brush with olive oil. Top with your favourite herbs or dukkah for extra flavour and bake until crisp.

IT'S NOT JUST BREAD. IT'S HELGA'S®
TRADITIONAL WHOLEMEAL
- Lower in Sodium†
- Source of Fibre
- Source of Protein
- 70% of the Whole Grain Daily Target Intake^
- Suitable for Vegans
- No Artificial Colours, Flavours or Preservatives
- No Added Sugar
- Health Star Rating 3.5 and Health Star Rating Chart

†30% less sodium than other leading brands compared to 620mg/100g average for 80% of the wraps market (January 2020).
^One serve (1 wrap) of Helga's Wholemeal Wraps contributes 70% towards the Grains & Legumes Nutrition Council™ 48g Whole Grain Daily Target Intake.

Products.RichDescription:
Helga's Spinach & Herb Wraps are thin, round and flat. They are 10 inches in diameter, a light green colour with visible spinach & herb flecks and golden brown toast marks. They are very soft and pliable texture making it a multipurpose wrap.

Helga's bakers begin with care by selecting the best quality ingredients, those that bring our the best taste in each other. The delicious combination of spinach along with thyme, rosemary, marjoram, basil, oregano and sage, is perfect to enhance your wrap.

WHY NOT TRY?
Use wraps to make cannelloni. Fill rolled wraps with your choice of ingredients such as mixed mushrooms and mozzarella cheese. Cover with sauce and sprinkle with cheese. Bake until piping hot and golden.
